  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the effect of combinative induction therapy with
      mitoxantrone and plasmapheresis versus induction therapy with mitoxantrone alone in cases of
      aggressive multiple sclerosis
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
